## Template Rules
- Under 150 words total
- Personalized first line is mandatory — never start with "I hope this finds you well"
- Reference specific pain points from gtm-os.yaml segments[].pain_points
- Use tone from segments[].voice.tone and segments[].voice.style
- Use key phrases from segments[].voice.key_phrases
- Avoid phrases from segments[].voice.avoid_phrases
- No mention of attachments
- Soft CTA only — ask a question, don't push a meeting
- If research brief exists for target, reference specific findings
